  ph.d. pre-application  
if you are interested in applying to the ph.d. program please fill out this
pre-application and email it to
phd@cs.cornell.edu.

  ph.d. application guide  
the guide gives you complete 
information on our department phd application process.  a hardcopy of this 
guide is what
will be sent to you, along with the application itself and other information, 
after you have completed the pre-application process.

  ph.d. requirements  
the requirements for the ph.d. in computer science are listed here.


